660
01:20:54,393 --> 01:20:57,328
The court
finds guilty the defendants

661
01:20:57,396 --> 01:21:00,058
Rita Beckhart, Caroline Steinhoff,

662
01:21:00,133 --> 01:21:02,601
Regina Kroit, Angela Zeva

663
01:21:02,668 --> 01:21:04,932
and Andrea Lumen

664
01:21:05,004 --> 01:21:09,941
