in 300 cases.

665
01:21:10,009 --> 01:21:12,876
The court finds guilty the defendant

666
01:21:12,945 --> 01:21:17,609
Hanna Schmitz of murder in 300 cases.

667
01:21:21,888 --> 01:21:24,982
The court sentences
the accused as follows:

668
01:21:25,057 --> 01:21:28,185
Rita Beckhart, Caroline Steinhoff,

669
01:21:28,261 --> 01:21:32,994
Regina Kroit, Angela Zeva
and Andrea Lumen

670
01:21:33,065 --> 01:21:38,435
