I said I'll tell you when we get there.

677
01:22:30,856 --> 01:22:35,452
- You told me you liked surprises.
- I like surprises.

678
01:22:53,246 --> 01:22:55,441
She's grown, hasn't she?

679
01:22:57,216 --> 01:23:01,016
I don't know. It's so long since
I saw her, Michael. How can I tell?

680
01:23:03,256 --> 01:23:07,556
It's my fault.
We shouldn't have come unannounced.

681
01:23:07,627 --> 01:23:10,790
Daddy's going to live
in his own house.

682
01:23:13,966 --> 01:23:17,197
Mother, I'm afraid
I have some bad news.

683
